1
00:00:07,657 --> 00:00:09,480
-Good morning!   -Hi.
-早上好!   -嗨.

2
00:00:09,613 --> 00:00:10,781
Welcome back.
欢迎回来.

3
00:00:10,912 --> 00:00:11,858
Did you have a good trip?
旅行愉快吗?

4
00:00:12,013 --> 00:00:15,521
Wonderful. Wonderful and very productive.
很棒. 很棒并且很有成果

5
00:00:15,665 --> 00:00:17,619
You didn't work the whole time, did you?
你没有一直在工作, 对不对?

6
00:00:17,742 --> 00:00:20,204
No. We had time to explore.
No. 我们有时间去探索.

7
00:00:20,354 --> 00:00:23,393
We wandered around Prague quite a bit.
我们在布拉格闲逛了不少.

8
00:00:23,573 --> 00:00:25,101
What a city.
多美的一座城市.

9
00:00:25,263 --> 00:00:27,079
It's supposed to be beautiful.
它应该是很美的.

10
00:00:27,201 --> 00:00:28,002
It is. 
确实如此.

11
00:00:28,151 --> 00:00:31,314
The hotel was right in the center of the old city.
酒店就在老城的中心.

12
00:00:31,455 --> 00:00:34,263
We walked everywhere. We shopped.
我们到处走. 我们购物.

13
00:00:34,409 --> 00:00:36,557
We went to some fine restaurants.
我们去了一些很好的餐厅.

14
00:00:36,681 --> 00:00:37,464
But even better,
但更好的是, 

15
00:00:37,603 --> 00:00:38,983
we went to a little lake.
我们去了一个小湖边.

16
00:00:39,115 --> 00:00:39,912
Where?
哪里?

17
00:00:40,054 --> 00:00:43,198
About 60 miles northwest of Prague.
大概60英里 布拉格的西北方.

18
00:00:43,415 --> 00:00:44,904
Near Karlovy Vary.
靠近Karlovy Vary.

19
00:00:45,248 --> 00:00:48,319
It was surrounded by farms and forests.
它被农场和森林包围着.

20
00:00:48,459 --> 00:00:49,516
And hills too,
还有山,

21
00:00:49,665 --> 00:00:51,187
though they weren't very high.
不过它们不是很高.

22
00:00:51,346 --> 00:00:53,245
We had a wonderful picnic.
我们享用了一个美妙的野餐.

23
00:00:53,387 --> 00:00:55,362
No one was there but us.
那儿一个人都没有 除了我们.

24
00:00:55,696 --> 00:00:57,413
Did you work at all?
你到底工作了没有?

25
00:00:57,566 --> 00:00:58,449
Oh yes.
Oh yes. 

26
00:00:58,598 --> 00:01:01,191
You and I can talk about that right now.
你和我可以谈谈关于那个 马上.

27
00:01:01,316 --> 00:01:04,082
You don't have plans for lunch, do you?
你没有计划对于午餐, 对吗?

28
00:01:05,597 --> 00:01:06,603
Time to go.
该走了.

